---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout lang="en" title="Services" description="Corporate video and content production for companies. Strategically conceived, cinematically produced. Brand films, interviews, social media content, and events.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-black pt-32">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-heading mb-6">Strategic video production for companies that want results.</h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-brand-light/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto">From concept to finished delivery. We combine cinematic craft with a clear understanding of your business goals.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- POSITIONIERUNG -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-dark">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6 text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          First Up Productions is a video and content studio focused on corporate clients. We work as an external production partner for companies and organisations that want to lift their visual communication to a professional level — through a structured process from concept and planning to production and delivery.
        </p>
        <p>
          The goal is not just a good video. The goal is content that strengthens your company, convinces, and shapes your professional presence over the long term. That is why we think along from day one: What is the communication goal? Who do we want to reach? Where will the content be used? What should it trigger? Only once those questions are answered does the actual production begin. That is how content gets made that genuinely works for your company.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CONTENT-FORMATE: VIER SÄULEN EINES ANGEBOTS -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-black">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="text-center mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-4">What we produce for you</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-muted max-w-2xl mx-auto">The right content for your company. Strategically conceived, professionally executed.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Intro Box -->
      <div class="mb-16">
        <div class="bg-brand-dark p-8 md:p-10 border border-brand-accent/15 text-center">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-3">Results that fit your company.</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-brand-muted leading-relaxed max-w-3xl mx-auto">
            The following formats show what we typically produce for our clients. At the same time: every project is developed individually based on your goals, your needs, and the type of collaboration that makes the most sense for you. We define scope, setup, and outcome together.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <!-- Brand presence -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-4">Brand presence</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Corporate films, image videos, and brand films: films that position your company professionally. For your website, campaigns, recruiting, and your entire corporate communication. The visual foundation on which your brand becomes visible.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-brand-muted">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Corporate films & company portraits</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Product videos & explainer formats</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Recruiting & employer-branding films</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Campaign content for web and social</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Interviews & Corporate communication -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-4">Interviews & corporate communication</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Employees, leaders, clients — professionally captured and shaped so that your voices build trust and your company culture becomes visible. One of the most effective formats for credibility and closeness.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-brand-muted">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Employee portraits & team voices</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Client voices & testimonials</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Leadership interviews & thought leadership</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Social Media & Business Content -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-4">Social media & business content</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            LinkedIn videos, reels, short-form formats, professionally produced and tailored to the channels where your audience actually is. Content that works across multiple platforms and puts your company on the map where it matters.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-brand-muted">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Reels, shorts & story formats</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> LinkedIn videos & thought pieces</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Behind-the-scenes & inside looks</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <!-- Event coverage -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-heading text-brand-accent mb-4">Event & company coverage</h3>
          <p class="text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed mb-4">
            Conferences, corporate events, trade shows — documented and reusable as content for your ongoing communication. So the event keeps working well beyond the day itself and becomes a lasting part of your corporate communication.
          </p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-brand-muted">
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Aftermovies & highlight films</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Speaker recordings & interviews</li>
            <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-brand-accent mt-1">—</span> Recap videos & social clips</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FLEXIBLES SETUP -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-dark">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading mb-6">A production setup that adapts to your company</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-light/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-8">
        Every company has different requirements. That is why we adapt the setup to what your project actually needs — from a compact shoot to a more elaborate production, from an efficient content session to a multi-day project. The right setup for the right result. From a single shoot day, formats for website, recruiting, internal communication, and social media can emerge. Where it fits the project, complementary photography can be produced on request.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-brand-muted">
        <span class="px-4 py-2 border border-white/10">Flexible camera setups</span>
        <span class="px-4 py-2 border border-white/10">Multi-cam when needed</span>
        <span class="px-4 py-2 border border-white/10">Professional sound & lighting</span>
        <span class="px-4 py-2 border border-white/10">Adaptable to scope & budget</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- LAUFENDE ZUSAMMENARBEIT -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-black border-y border-white/5">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading mb-6">Also as an ongoing partnership.</h2>
          <p class="text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Do you need not just a single video but regular professional content for your company — for social media, recruiting, internal communication, or your website?
          </p>
          <p class="text-brand-light/70 leading-relaxed">
            Then let's talk about an ongoing collaboration: fixed shoot days per month or quarter, different formats out of a single shoot, consistent quality, and a production partner who knows your brand and thinks along strategically. Fully plannable, reliable, and at your level.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <h3 class="text-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-brand-accent mb-4">What that means in practice:</h3>
          {[
            'Plannable shoot days, plannable outcomes',
            'Different formats from a single shoot',
            'Consistent visual language across all channels',
            'Conceptual support included',
            'A lasting point of contact who thinks along',
          ].map(item => (
            <div class="flex items-start gap-4 text-brand-light/70 text-sm">
              <span class="text-brand-accent mt-0.5 shrink-0">—</span>
              <p>{item}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="section-padding bg-brand-black">
    <div class="container-narrow text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-heading mb-6">Let's talk about your project.</h2>
      <p class="text-brand-light/60 max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">No commitment, personal, direct. Tell us what you have in mind and we'll tell you honestly how we can help.</p>
      <a href="/en/contact" class="btn-primary">Schedule a first call</a>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
